name: Neon Rain
description: I am excited for the release of this cinemagraph and very first collaboration with Lucius. This photo was taken at Tachikawa, Tokyo - a train station known for great Japanese izakaya and bars. The inspiration behind this collaboration was to take a real life moment in Japan and recreate an anime-like scene through our vision. Twitter: @lllonilll (photography/soundscape), @luciusfelimus (animation)
